commit.message: Update Changes in preparation for release 1.11

More careful determination of whether ocamlopt is available

The Makefile.config variable `NATIVE_COMPILER` does not exist prior to 4.10.
The Makefile.config variable `ARCH` can be different from `none` yet
ocamlopt can be disabled since 4.12.
Testing a combination of both variables should be robust enough.

Fixes: #34

Generate and install .mli .cmt .cmti files

Closes: #32
Update tests and add automatic test harness
Convert README to Markdown and update it

Add local .opam file

Taken from earlier versions and updated.

Build in "opt" (native-code) mode automatically

make all does make allopt if supported
Use `Stdlib.` instead of `Pervasives.`

Update META file to use plugin convention (#33)

The `archive(native,plugin)` convention was used before ocamlfind defined one using `plugin`

commit.message:
Zip.add_entry_generator ~level:0 was missing a CRC update

Closes: #29
Update Changes for release 1.10

Fixup flush_continue command to use the correct flush method (#25)

This commit fixes up the new flush_continue method to use the FLUSH_SYNC setting rather than the FINAL setting (which meant that the Zlib instance could not be reused after running flush_continue.
Build test/testzlib as part of the default test build
fix testzlib.ml  (String=>Bytes) (#24)
Tweak documentation comments

Adapt to caml_named_value signature change (#23)

Since OCaml 4.09, `caml_named_value` now returns a `const char *`.
Updates for release 1.09

Add a `flush_continue` function (#22)

Add a flush_continue function that allows the user to flush the contents of the zip buffer all the way to disk but then continue writing to the zipped channel.
Updates for release 1.08
More files to ignore

Failing assert when reading large zip files (#16)

Number of files in archive is stored in 2 bytes, so it needs to be taken mod 2^16 in some checks.

Also: opam fails with missing install-findlib job, so alias it with "install"

Closes: #15

Close file descriptors when exception is raised (#18)

Closes: #17
Zlib.compress_direct should call deflate_end (#13)
Add versions of Zlib.deflate and Zlib.inflate with input buffers as immutable strings (#14)

INSTALLDIR variable is no longer used

... since we switched to ocamlfind install.

Better URL for Zlib

Closes #12
Add a gitignore file for build artifacts (#10)
